reviewText: This was hilarious!  Great movie! The characters were real and were based on African Americans I know.  Especially the mom telling the children to take out the decorations for the tree.  I laughed so hard!  We all know somebody's mother like that.
Oh my goodness, I am so glad I bought this movie. The kids aboslutely love it! They watched it over and over again!
My grandchild like it, she sat still and watched it all the way through. It was funny, entertaining, and a cast of characters that she recognize from different programs.  She loved it, I liked it.

I recently purchased this along with Thugaboo to watch with my nieces. They are seven and eight and enjoyed watching this movie. What I enjoyed most was the message that it taught at the end of the movie. So not only was it funny but there was also a lesson to be learned. To bad the Wayan's family didn't make more movies.
This is an awesome dvd, the Grandkids just love it. It keeps the little ones very attentative. Recommend that you purchase this along with Thugaboo Sneakers Attack by the Wayans.
